measurements.description: Four overall flat lily form flowers on one erect 40.0-cm inflorescence; sepals chartreuse blushed maroon, veined maroon, mid-vein darker maroon; petals porrect, chartreuse blushed maroon along margins, veined maroon, mid-vein darker maroon; lip cream, side lobes overlaid light burgundy, centrally spotted burgundy, crest yellow distally; column light green, darker marginally, ventral surface blotched burgundy, anther cap cream; substance firm; texture satiny, lip matte.
